question: Where can I find fast food restaurant on the way to Alejandra von Hartz Gallery, Miami, FL within 60 kilometers from 60 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-80.470734 25.614343)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-80.19926 25.802075)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'fast_food'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-80.470734 25.614343)',4326)::geography, 60000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-80.470734 25.614343)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);

[4].display_name: Alejandra von Hartz Gallery, Miami, FL
